{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas atgreeſahs pee fa-\nweem Brahteem/ un ſazzija: tas\nPuifenſtur newaid/ un eß/ kur\nbuhs man palikt?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee nehine Jahſepa\nSwahrkus/ un nokawe Ahſi/ un\napmehrze tohs Swahrkus Affini.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee noſuhtija tohs raſ-\nbus Swahrkus/ un likke tohs\nfatwam Tehwam noneſt/ un ſaz-\nzija: Schohs effaim mehß atrad-\nduſchi/ apraugi jelle/ woj tee ta-\nwa Dehla Swahrki/ jeb ne?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas paſinne tohs/ un ſaz-\nzija : tee irr manna Dehla\nSwahrki/ nikns Swehrs irr\nvinau aprihjis/ ſaplohtiht irr\ntas Jahſepu ſaplohtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs pahrplehſe\nawas Dreheſes/un apwilke Mai-\nſit apfahrt fatweem Gurneem/\nun behdajahß pehz fatvn Dehlu\nilgu Laiku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahß wiſſi winna\nDehli/ un wiſſas winna Mettas/\nto eepeezihaft / bet wiſſch ne\ngribbejahß eepeezinajauns / un ſaz-\nzija: Eſktuhſchu behdadams\npee manna Dehla Bedrê / un\nwinna Tehws apraudaja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Midijaniteri pahr-\ndeive to Egiptes-Semmê/Poti-\nwaram/ ta Kehnina Warniis\nKambar-Junkuram un Annei-\nsterain.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas notikke tanni\nLaika/ kad Juhda no fa-\nweem Brahteem no\nOdollamitera Wihrn/ Jhra-\nWahrda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Juhda redſeja tur kaſ-\nda Kananitera Wihra Meitu,\nun winnas Wahrds bija Sud-\nun wiſſch nehnie to/ un gahje pe-\ntahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta tappe gruhta / u-\ndſemdeja weenu Dehlu / un no-\nſauze winna Wahrdugers.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta tappe atkaſ gruhta\nun dſemdeja weenu Dehlu/ u-\nnoſauze winna Wahrdud Onans\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta dſinnahß wehl pro-\njam/ un dſemdeja weenu Dehlu\nun noſauze winna Wahrdud See-\nlus/ un wiſſch bija Kesibâ / ka-\nwinna to dſemdeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Juhda nehme ween\nSeewu preekſch Gerru fawn pin-\ndſintu/ un winnas Wahrdub bij-\nTahmare.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Gers/ Juhda Piru-\ndſinitais bija niens ta KUD-\nGA Preekſcha/ tapehz nofan-\nto tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad ſazzija Juhda us O-\nnanu : Eij pee tawa Bra-\nSeewas/un nem to tawa Bra-\nta Weetâ/ un zell tawain Bra-\ntam Dſinnumunu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Onans finnadams\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
